=head1 NAME

cbr2pdf - Convert .cbr files to PDF (short alias for convert-cbr-to-pdf)

=head1 VERSION

This document describes version 0.003 of cbr2pdf (from Perl distribution App-EbookUtils), released on 2025-10-26.

